N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8121.00 - General

State Regulations
(a) Route 20. Route
20 between the Oneida-Herkimer county line and the Otsego-Herkimer county line
in the Village of West Winfield and the Town of Winfield. (b) Dyke Road, CR 37. Dyke Road, CR 37, between Route 5 and Bleecker Street, CR 241, in the Towns of Schuyler and

Frankfort. (d) Route 5. Route 5
between the Oneida-Herkimer county line and the Montgomery-Herkimer county line
in the City of Little Falls and the Village of Herkimer and the Towns of

Schuyler, Herkimer, Little Falls, and Manheim. (e) Route 5S. Route 5S between the

Oneida-Herkimer county line and Route 167 in the Villages of Frankfort, Ilion, and Mohawk and the Towns of Frankfort, German Flatts and Little

Falls. (f) Route 167. Route 167
between Route 5S and Route 5 in the City of Little Falls and the Town of Little

Falls. (g) [Eff. until Feb. 28, 1996, see also subd. (g) below.] Route 28. Route 28 between Route 5S and Route
5, in the Villages of Herkimer and Mohawk. (g) [Eff. Feb. 28, 1996, see also subd. (g)
above.] Route 28. Route 28 between Route 5 and the Herkimer-Otsego county line
in the Village of Herkimer and Mohawk and the Towns of German Flatts, Columbia
and Warren. (i) Route 167. Route
167 between Route 5 and Route 29, in the City of Little Falls, the Village of

Dolgeville and the Town of Manheim. (j) Route 169. Route 169 between IR 90 (Exit
29A) and Route 5, in the City of Little Falls and the Town of Danube. Notes
